Skit makers, Great Egbuchulam known as Clean-Mumu, Solomon Mbata, known as Baggy_Universe and Arinze Mbah known as Dat_Skirtboi have denied eating faeces in a video that went viral on social media.
They claimed they were only making a comedy skit.
According to News Agency Of Nigeria, the skit makers denied involvement with Internet fraud, adding that they were completely misunderstood after an anonymous passer-by recorded the video, causing it to go viral on social media.
“We were not eating faeces as many persons believe but, we were portraying the extent to which many persons, especially youths, have gone in a bid to acquire wealth,” Mbah said.
